  <brief_title>Chemotherapy Plus Proton-chemotherapy for Locally Advanced Pancreatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of Gemcitabine and Erlotinib (GE) Plus Proton-chemotherapy (PCT) and Capox for Locally Advanced Pancreatic Cancer (LAPC)</official_title>
